text: Liu Yanan (, born 25 February 1992) is a Chinese professional racing cyclist. She rides for China Chongming-Liv-Champion System Pro Cycling. She is from Heilongjiang. ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female cyclists Category:Cyclists from Heilongjiang
